original_title: My way oder Die Mistkübel haben Angst vor der Leere
overview: Haymon Maria Buttinger, a legendary Austrian prop master, singer and actor. A showman in front of the camera and his great dream of being Macbeth, Quasimodo and Jeckyll-Hyde just once. The portrait of a friend.
title: My way oder Die Mistkübel haben Angst vor der Leere
